σ\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Θεσ\">ΘΕΣ\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic030092_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic030092_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic030092.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic030092-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text after Bettarini.\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Two names, e.g. in -λοχος and Θεστ- (or e.g. Θεσσαλός?), respectively, ed.pr., who underlines that these meagre contents are no compelling evidence to classify the document as a defixio (though the lead speaks in favor of this interpretation). (SEG)\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Nulla indica che il frammento in questione sia una defixio: il fatto di essere un frammento plumbeo tuttavia costituisce un valido argomento in favore della sua possibile classificazione, anche se il dubbio rimane. (Bettarini)\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 55.1026 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Bettarini 2005 6 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001388\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001388\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp>lunate sigma and very small omicron in triangular form.\u003C/p>  Line 1  4  \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[210,213,216,219,222,224,227,230,233],{"id":211,"html":212},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Savannah Neibart\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"οχος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"idionym\" data-text=\"οχος\">[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cspan data-text=\"οχος\">οχος\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"καὶ\">καὶ\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Θεσ\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"idionym\" data-text=\"Θεσ\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Θεσ\">Θεσ\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Savannah Neibart\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"atteste